# Keep Nx project graph / @nx/expo hashing away from huge native trees and caches.
# Without this, `nx dev web` can fail with: Invalid string length (@nx/expo/plugin)
# when apps/mobile/android/** exists (local `expo run:android` / prebuild output).

apps/mobile/android/**
apps/mobile/ios/**
apps/mobile/.expo/**
apps/mobile/dist/**
apps/mobile/out-tsc/**
